<br>
some things to keep in mind.<br>
<br>
1. slow spells take time to cast and IF the enchanter is mezing and slowing, they first mez then slow generally<br>
<br>
2. slow are incredibly effective, ive seen a warrior pull and once the mob is mezed and a shaman slows, they lose no more hp.... this due to regen, mark of karn spell and garou spell and blood point weapons.<br>
<br>
